      <title>高盛（Goldman Sachs</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-12/goldman-sachs-says-us-credit-spreads-will-get-a-lot-wider</link>
      <description><![CDATA[高盛集团公司（Goldman Sachs Group Inc.）的战略家大幅提高了他们对美国信贷差价的预测，理由是关税风险和迹象表明白宫愿意容忍短期的经济弱点。]]></description>
